text: Jaime René Pinto Bravo (born 9 October 1939) is a retired professional tennis player from Chile. He reached his career-high singles ranking of World No. 73 in August 1973. ==Life== Jaime Pinto Bravo was born in Chile and he played in Davis Cup for Chile. His daughter Anita Pinto is a professional squash player. ==References== ==External links== * * * * Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean male tennis players
